{"type": "article", "id": 30530, "title": "毛毡桌面隔断", "description": "", "date": "2016-08-03T23:04:40Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 6, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160803164830aARMfThBWSVDzI2j.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>这个让人联想到图书馆自习桌的桌面隔断是比利时设计师 Pierre-Emmanuel Vandeputte 的作品，橡木框架中固定了一片折叠起来的毛毡，当中的空间可以用来存放小物。相比塑料或者金属制的隔断，浅色毛毡和橡木的组合给人的感觉更柔和温软，简洁的造型适用于各种开放式的办公环境。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160803164900DN6vecjRr23fOyxk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160803164903GpVB4EjNrHoqcF6d.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666471\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160803164902lxkRvHN1L5YMJmVF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160803164901Km8ApveX6g43Vray.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}